:

*Ozbiljno* je vreme za rad na projektu. (This is a serious time for working on the project.)
Učenje stranog jezika je *ozbiljan* zadatak. (Learning a foreign language is a serious task.)
Moraš *ozbiljno* razmisliti o svojoj budućnosti. (You must seriously think of your future.)
On je *ozbiljan* čovek koji ne voli šalu. (He is a serious man who does not like jokes.)
On je *ozbiljno* povređen. (He is seriously injured.)